vote.title: An ordinance abandoning an alley to Forest Forward and Forest Theater, LLC, the abutting owner, containing approximately 3,011 square feet of land, located near the intersection of South Central Expressway and Peabody Avenue; and authorizing the quitclaim - Revenue: General Capital Reserve Fund ($9,809.00) and General Fund ($20,000.00), plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
